To mirror a table in a sheet you can use 'Paste link' to paste the values of another sheet.
This will mirror your table in another sheet

You may want to change the cell format as some zero may appear instead of blank cells.
You can format it with 'FOrmat cells' and choose 'Custom'

0;-0;;@
with this to remove the zeros

You can also use 'Paste linked image' but this will paste an image that will mirroring your table
